values:
One more day and then I'm on vacation.  After 230 tomorrow I'm offically off for one week.  YEA!!! I hate my job.  I really don't like the people I work with.  Correction, they are decent people outside of work but at work they are just complete morons. AH!

Being at work all day everyday with no interaction with anyone has really given me time to think.  I've come to a couple conclusions.  I'm kind of glad I'm single.  I don't know how to behave myself when I'm in a relationship.  Not that I cheat or anything.  I've only cheated on two of the people I've ever dated. Remy and Bryan.  But anyway.  I just don't know how to act.  I always isolate myself from my friends and spend every waking moment with whomever I'm dating.  I also have fits of anger and take it out on them.  I do that to my friends too.  I don't know how people put up with me.  But Duckie and Judi have said that I am getting better. 

I have to learn how to handle relationships.  It's just something I have to learn how to do so that I don't piss anyone off anymore.  Time to grow up I guess, all that jazz.  I just realized this this morning.  I was thinking about my other relationships and why they ended and it all came down to one thing.  My attitude.  I mean it wasn't entirely my fault but my attitude has played a big part in my relationships.  Christina was always bitching at me cause of my attitude.  Maybe it's time that I change that. I want to change.  I'm not doing it for other people though, I'm doing it for myself so I can be a better person.  I want to be a better person.  I think that if I really try I can do it.  Hope for the best.

You know I think it's just better if I remain single for oh let's say the rest of my life. I just keep making bad choices. They seem alright at the time but then I come to realize that it's not alright or I end up hurting. I'm just gonna keep to myself. 

I thought maybe he had changed. Well he did change but he still has his some of his old habits that I just can't stand. Like telling me he's gonna call me and doesn't then ends up giving me an excuse that's really fucking lame. I don't think this is gonna work out anymore. I talked to him last night and he said he was gonna take care of the little obstacle in our way but I don't even know if he did that. I've heard these things one too many times. I was forced fed the "baby this time will be differnt" senario too many times to believe it anymore. My faith in men isn't there anymore. I know all the lines and I hate them.

I'm glad we're friends, I really am.  Maybe it's just better that way. I'm just not the kinda girl that you date I guess. oh well, not my problem.

Have you ever passed by my house,
Hoping to catch a glimpse of me.
Have you ever smelled my perfume,
And thought I was near by.
Have you ever looked at my picture,
Just so you could see my face.
Have you ever picked up the phone,
Only to dial my number and hang up.
Have you ever dreamt of me,
Only to wake up and realize you can't have me anymore.
Have you ever longed to have me in your arms,
Only to realize that you can't.
Have you ever looked at your new girlfriend,
And almost called her by my name.
Have you ever wished to just hear my voice one time,
Just to remember that you keep pushing me away and can't.
Have you ever woken up in the morning,
Only to see that I'm not next to you.
Have you ever regretted giving me up,
And remembered it was our stubbornness that drove us apart.
Have you ever wished that it was me you were with,
Instead of this other girl.
Have you ever wanted to get back together,
But were too afraid to admit you were wrong.

You still linger in my mind,
Refusing to go away.
I tell myself you never loved me,
As if that would make it easier.
I tell myself I'm better off without you,
But I still want you by my side.
I love you,
Even though I don't want to.
I long to hold you,
To kiss you and hold you close.
I miss feeling safe in your arms,
I miss laughing together.
Do you even think of those times,
Or does your mind linger on the bad times.
Do you let yourself think of me,
Or did you really erase me.
If I could tell you one thing it would be this,
I will always love you.

Yeah I'm in a mood right now. Oh boy do I feel like taking my anger out on someone. Well not someone, someone in particular. I feel like going off on her and just fucking making her feel all the pain that I have trapped in my heart. I feel like a bomb ready to explode. I've been on the brink of it since August. Now my fuse is slowly burning towards the bottom. I just wanna go off somewhere tonight and break shit. I need to be destructive. If I don't do something I'm gonna turn on myself and I'll start the whole vicious cycle. fuck me. 

To top it all off, I'm having all these weird feelings towards a friend of mine and it's just not cool to have these feelings. They know too much about me. But damnit they won't go away. I can't stop them. I just finally admitted what people were telling me all along and I want it to disappear. I want it to go away!! But I like impossible situations, cause I like to have something to complain about. Someone said that to me I forget who it was, but they are fucking wrong. But whatever.

Back to this exploding thing. What set me off, you don't even want to know. Let's just say she's about 5 foot 8 or 9 with brown hair and big brown eyes. Need a bigger hint, SHE USE TO LOVE ME. I have been thinking about her alot the past few weeks, well the past month and half. It's like she's stuck in my damn head. I wanna take a power drill, put it to my temple and drill her out of my head. Then maybe I'll get some peace and quiet up there so I can think. Every time things get quiet all I hear in my head is her telling me how much she loves me and how we're gonna be happy together. I hear her promising that she'll never leave me. NEVER LEAVE ME HUH???? Seems like ya did. I mean I tried and tried and tried. Then i gave up. Then my damn birthday came along.

Why did she have to send me those flowers. Why? Cause she knew it would make me weaken, cause I'm weak. Well not anymore. NO more crying, No more tears, No more pining away, NO MORE YOU. Never leave me huh? Ha! Yeah right. You dropped me for that girl faster then I could say Hey. Story of my life. There's always someone better than me, prettier than me, YOUNGER than me, thinner than me, and the list goes on and on. 

How easily I was replaced. That goes to show you how important our relationship was. I bet every single thing she told me she's telling her new little princess right now. AHH fuck it they deserve each other. I'd rather DIE then deal with posers and people who spout off the same generic lines to ALL of their g/fs.

As you use to say to me all the time "No one likes a whiner" So I'm done.

"fuck you, fuck you, fuck you, you're cool, fuck you. I'm out."

People are soooooooo funny. Drama, drama, drama. I just hope it all stops cause man this is nuts. We all say things that are not called for in the heat of the moment, me included. Especially me, i'm the queen of foot in mouth syndrome. I'm sorry if I hurt people's feelings, truely I am. That's all i can say. That's all I will say. I won't justify myself to perfect strangers for my craziness. And neither should they. To quote the old man from muppets take manhattan (has anyone seen that movie besides me? LoL) Peoples is Peoples. I will do my best to keep my damn mouth shut and be civil as long as everyone else does too. Let's just call it a truce. Cool?

I'm really sick of people. Really! It's crazy when I have to make an appointment to see someone who is suppose to be my best friend. I give up. I really do. Fuck making appointments and shit, I shouldn't have to do that. They got pissed at me last year when I kept blowing them off and all they do is blow me off. Yeah okay dude, that makes perfect sense. I've apologized numerous times for blowing people off when I was with Christina. What about you???? You've been doing more than blowing me off. You blow everyone off but your signicant other. And you're changing into something that isn't you. You don't make your own decisions anymore, or even act as social as you use to be. Eveytime we hang out you hardly talk, that is if we actually have time to hang out just the two of us. It hasn't been just the two of us for awhile. Fuck this I'll see if we can do it next week shit. I'm going through a lot of shit lately and need my best friend. But whatever dude it's alright. Go on discluding all of your friends from  your life. If shit comes crashing down and you have no one to go to or a shoulder to cry on remember it was you who pushed us all away. We don't know who you are anymore.

Call me bitchy or whatever but I'm sorry I've been holding this in for too damn long. It had to be said. So I'm sorry if I'm being harsh but sometimes life is harsh.

Sue me I've been busy lately, or just really haven't felt like posting so I didn't. But I have been having a decent time. 

Last Thursday I went to go see Twisted Sister with Andy and Hector. I was sooooo excited. I mean come on, how long have I been in love with Dee Snider. That's all I could talk about for weeks when I heard that he was playing after pretty suicide awhile ago. But I didn't get to go to that show. Ever since then I've been patiently waiting for someone to find out if or when Twisted Sister or just Dee would be playing. Finally Andy pulled through. So Andy, Hector and I went to the Meadowland's fair grounds and saw Twisted motherfucking Sister. It was AWESOME. i love Dee Snider even more then I use to. The orginal band was there in all their Twisted Sister make-up and out fits, it was great. I had so much fun.

Friday was the fourth. Blah, Blah, Blah. Fireworks and my cousin Mel came and visited me. Todd came with her. He's such a wonderful guy. I'm so glad that they are still together. It's nice to see that sometimes relationships CAN work out even though there are arguments. But anyway. They slept over. We all had fun.

Monday I went to a concert. Missy Elliot was there. Busta Rhymes, Fabolous(:P),50-cent, Jay-Z. It was nice. Fabolous sucked. Jay-Z got boring. MIssy was good. Busta was better. I had a good time. Few glitches but I don't want to talk about them.

But anyway. I'll be working more starting in September. So I guess if you want to see me you should see me before then cause the only free time i have is after work or on weekends. But I gotta do what I gotta do. Whatever. More soon. Later.
